<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_559" id="278v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_559_r2l1">Den <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd Reͣten / Des <expan>Heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Reıchs Stette </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l2"><expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> Vlme . <expan>Nördlıng<ex>en</ex></expan> Rotweıl <expan>Mem<ex>m</ex>ingen</expan> vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l3"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>mıteınand<ex>er</ex></expan> ın eynung ſınd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_559_r2l4"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns yecʒ <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> von der <expan>gelegenh<ex>eit</ex></expan> eẅrs <expan>geleg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vor ʒolr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l5"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> als der Hochgeborn fürſt <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> karl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ʒog</expan> ʒu <expan>Luttrıng<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> in kürcʒ <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l7">Jm darauf <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>umb</expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> habt . in <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> geſandt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l8">habt etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ſol vns eẅr <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l9">getrawen . Daʒ wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeͣhen daʒ es eẅch gelüklıch vnd wol ergıeng </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l10">vnd ob wır ıcht rede <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> hören <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır eẅch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu gut dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l11">Jnn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> als vıl vns gebürt / ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır auch <expan>keıne<ex>m</ex></expan> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> der wır mechtıg <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> . <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hengen</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſtatte<ex>n</ex></expan> hılff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l13">oder beyſtant <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> darinn ʒutun <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>r</expan> wır des gewar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l14">wurden . Denn von ſamnung vnd <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>bs</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc VVıſſen noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l15">hören wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> von keinr <expan>ſamnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> in der gegend vmb vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l16">VVır wellen <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vorſch darnach haben . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l17">erfüren wır ıcht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr dauon / dıe vns <expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>deẅchte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l18"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> . Das <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>furderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_r2l19">wır das <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt auch ʒu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben . Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_line_1592205554969_3125">wo wir <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_559_line_1592205557512_3130"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> dıe <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> thome <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_559" id="278v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und reͣten des
                                <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> reichs stette
                                <expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, Ulme,
                            <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>, Rotweil,
                            <expan>Mem<ex>m</ex>ingen</expan> und den
                        <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> in
                        eynung sind, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns yecz
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> von der <expan>gelegenh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        ewrs <expan>geleg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vor Zolr
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>, als der hochgeborn fürst,
                            <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Karl, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>zog</expan> zu
                                <expan>Luttring<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.,
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in kürcz <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ir im darauf
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> habt, in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan> gesandt habt etc., das haben wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu sol uns ewr
                                <expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawen, daz wir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> seͣhen, daz es ewch gelüklich und wol
                        ergieng, und, ob wir icht rede <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> hören
                                <expan>wurd<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir ewch
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu gut darinn
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>, als vil uns gebürt. So
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir auch
                            <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> der wir mechtig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
<expan>ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hengen</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gestatte<ex>n</ex></expan>, hilff oder beystant
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        darinn zu tun, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>r</expan> wir des gewar wurden. Denn
                        von samnung und <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>bs</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. wissen noch hören wir zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> von keinr
                            <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> in der gegend umb uns; wir wellen
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> vorsch darnach haben; und erfüren wir icht
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr davon, die uns
                                <expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dewchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan>, das
                            <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>furderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun, als wir das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst auch zu
                            <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> mass <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        haben. Denn wo wir <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> die <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome
                                <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
